  "elapsed_s": 85.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the last time of the ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after the Russian broke through the front of the Germans in Uman, the German army undertook a great retreat operation into Moldova, into Romania.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [INAUDIBLE] Podolsk, as Kamenetz-Podolsk, which is another city on the Dniester, became the key positions for this retreat, all the German and Romanian army, which were in Ukraine still or in Transnistria, had to withdraw on one of these two points.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Germans took over the entire operation they were commanding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to tell you the truth, I never saw an army retreating in such an order like the German army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Units, equipments, guns, everything in perfect order.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was working at that time in repairing the highways, the roofs, so the-- the access should be better, also is that [INAUDIBLE] organization.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the group that we worked in on the bridges, they had also some SS people as possible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were olderly-- elderly persons, mobilized during the war in Germany, and there was only they worked.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at the given day, they called me and some other people in and told us-- told us, sneak home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The SS is coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At hike as fast as you can.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't walk on the-- on the roads-- on the routes, but through the fields and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we somehow got back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then, the ghetto was over-flooded with German soldiers, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we were terribly afraid because we had some knowledge what happened with other places at the retreat of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were also Italian units, and we also looked for to be with the Italians.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
